  "landing.view.badgemuseumsubmit.button": "Submit",
  "landing.view.badgemuseumsubmit.header": "Show your Badges to your friends",
  "landing.view.badgemuseumvote.body": "The badge museums have arrived! Now we just need to work out who's is the best; is the one with the rarest badges or maybe the one with the most? You decide, get your votes in now. You'll need to have at least the Respected Hartix IV achievement to vote.",
