  "landing.view.blocksroombuilding.body": "Do you think you're the best Hartix Builder? Prove it. To welcome Building Blocks to the hotel, for the next week we will be hosting room building competitions! Get creative and you could win Builders' Club subscriptions and EXCLUSIVE badges!",
  "landing.view.blocksroombuilding.button": "Join the fun <Builders' Club warehouse>",
