  "landing.view.gallery_bundle3.body": "Get a red-hot piece of real estate and pick up three EXTREMELY valuable pieces of Hartix art at the same time with this bundle! Who WOULDN'T want Creation of Hartix by Frankaelangelo? Exclusive badge included",
  "landing.view.gallery_bundle3.button": "Check it out!",
