  "landing.view.jurassic15dragonfly.body": "WOAH - This colourful Meganeura LTD - that's a jurassic Dragonfly to you and me - is MEGA awesome. These gentle giants roam the Jurassic Hartix landscape, gliding through the Hotel air, flapping their delicate wings in a graceful but hurried way. Available in limited quantities, don't let this LTD fly away...",
