  "landing.view.leprechaun2.timer.expired": "The Leprechaun is in the Shop!",
  "landing.view.leprechaun2.timeremaining": "The Leprechaun is coming in...",
  "landing.view.library_bundle.body": "It's that long dreaded time of the year…exams are here! Don't sweat it, Hartix, you'll do great. Everyone knows distraction is the enemy of productivity, but that won't be true for long once you have...your own private library to study in! Packed to the ceiling with leather-bound books and soft seating, this bundle is sure to help you keep your head down and your grades UP! Includes badge.",
