  "landing.view.ny14bundle2.body": "DROP THE BRIDGE…and let in the warmth! This frosty winter castle comes equipped with all the ice-covered furni any royal Hartix could desire, from an ice covered motto to regally frosted turrets. Includes an EXCLUSIVE badge. Available 7th - 13th January",
  "landing.view.ny14bundle2.button": "Check it out!",
