  "landing.view.ny14catsale.body": "Brrr this winter has been cold. Let's heat things with a Hartix Catalogue sale! Only here for a short time, this annual SALE has it all! Don't miss out on big savings with this limited time offer. (*Check News article for corresponding days and sales!*)",
  "landing.view.ny14catsale.button": "Happy shopping",
