  "landing.view.xm14furniforbc.body": "EXCLUSIVE TO BUILDERS' CLUB! All the way from the snowy North Pole…Hartix Christmas furni is here! From Snowy Castles to City Skyscrapers and all the tinsel in between; a very Hartix Christmas is here. Get your Christmas festivities started early this year with Builders' Club..",
