  "nux.bot.bubble.duckets.1": "Did you know, in Hartix we have a currency that you earn every visit!? They're called Duckets!",
  "nux.bot.bubble.duckets.2": "You can use Duckets to buy furniture, decorations, and more pet food for your pet. Check out the <a href",
  "nux.bot.bubble.farewell.2": "Enjoy your stay, %username%!",
  "nux.bot.bubble.gift.fridge.1": "Here's your first one: a refrigerator that's always full! You can find it in your inventory.",
  "nux.bot.bubble.gift.fridge.2": "Place your new refrigerator on the floor, then double-click it to get a refreshment.",
  "nux.bot.bubble.gift.hc.1": "I have another gift for you today...a Hartix Club membership!",
  "nux.bot.bubble.gift.hc.2": "For the next 3 days you will have access to Hartix Club and all it's awesome features - like exclusive clothes and hairstyles!",
  "nux.bot.bubble.gift.pet.1": "Did you know we have pets in Hartix? Oh, yes! Everything from cats and dogs to pigs and even dragons!",
  "nux.bot.bubble.gift.pet.2": "For your gift today, you have three options. Please choose from the menu.",
  "nux.bot.bubble.gift.pet.promise.1": "Tomorrow I'll be giving you your very own pet - a cat, a dog or a pig!",
  "nux.bot.bubble.greeting.2": "Welcome back, %username%!",
  "nux.bot.bubble.hcpromo.1": "Have you enjoyed the Hartix Club? It is the ultimate way to express yourself and stand out from the crowd!",
  "nux.bot.bubble.hcpromo.2": "For the price of a soda you can join Hartix Club and get thousands of additional clothing, hair and accessory combinations!",
  "nux.bot.bubble.hcpromo.3": "You can extend your membership <a href",
  "nux.bot.day.1.step.1.bubble.0": "Welcome to Hartix, %username%! - I'm Frank, the Hotel manager. Click on the floor to walk and come on in, this is your home room!",
  "nux.bot.day.1.step.1.bubble.1": "Over the next few days, I will be giving you lots of free but valuable gifts!",
  "nux.bot.day.1.step.1.bubble.2.fridge": "Here's your first free gift - a refrigerator that's always full! You can find it in your inventory.",
  "nux.bot.day.1.step.1.bubble.2": "Would you like your first gift?",
  "nux.bot.day.1.step.2.bubble.1.fridge": "You can find your fridge by pressing the <a href",
  "nux.bot.day.1.step.2.bubble.2": "To place items in your room, simply drag them from your inventory.",
  "nux.bot.day.1.step.3.bubble.1.fridge": "After placing the refrigerator on the floor, double-click it to get a refreshment!",
  "nux.bot.day.1.step.3.bubble.1": "To place your TV, simply drag it from your inventory and put it down somewhere in your room.",
  "nux.bot.day.1.step.3.bubble.2": "Well, I've got to go greet the other guests - See you tomorrow! Please go explore the hotel on your own, tomorrow you'll get your very own pet - a cat, a dog or a pig!",
  "nux.bot.day.1.step.5.bubble.1": "Well, I've got to go greet the other guests. Please go explore the hotel on your own, tomorrow you'll get your very own pet - a cat, a dog or a pig!",
  "nux.bot.day.1.step.5.bubble.2": "See you tomorrow, %username%!",
  "nux.bot.day.2.step.1.bubble.1": "Hello, there! It's great to see you again. Welcome back!",
  "nux.bot.day.2.step.1.bubble.2": "Did you know we have pets in Hartix? Oh, yes! Everything from cats and dogs, to crocodiles, bears, frogs, pigs, monkeys and even monster plants!",
  "nux.bot.day.2.step.1.bubble.3": "For your gift today, you have three options! Please choose from the menu below.",
  "nux.bot.day.2.step.2.bubble.1": "Great choice! Check your <a href",
  "nux.bot.day.2.step.2.bubble.2": "Well, that's all I have for today - Tomorrow I'll give you a free membership to Hartix Club! See you then.",
  "nux.bot.day.2.step.2.bubble.3": "See you tomorrow, %username%!",
  "nux.bot.day.3.step.1.bubble.1": "Welcome back, %username%!",
  "nux.bot.day.3.step.1.bubble.2": "Ah, how is your pet? Hungry? In Hartix we have a second currency that you earn on every visit: Duckets! You can use it to buy more pet food from the <a href",
  "nux.bot.day.3.step.1.bubble.3.3day": "A 3-day Hartix Club membership!",
  "nux.bot.day.3.step.1.bubble.3": "As promised, I have a very special gift for you today.",
  "nux.bot.day.3.step.1.bubble.4": "Before I give you the membership, you'll need to verify your account via SMS text.",
  "nux.bot.day.3.step.1.bubble.5": "Don't worry, we won't send you any pesky marketing. Click me to find out more about SMS verification.",
  "nux.bot.day.3.step.2.bubble.1": "You now have access to Hartix Club and all it's amazing features for 3 days!",
  "nux.bot.day.3.step.2.bubble.2": "Why don't you try out a new outfit :)",
  "nux.bot.day.3.step.3.bubble.1": "Well, enjoy the rest of your day!",
  "nux.bot.day.3.step.3.bubble.2": "See you tomorrow, %username%!",
