  "quests.April_12_1.1332494992306.hint": "We need trustworthy, skilled Commanders for a special responsibility...a secret mission of sorts! Of course we can't tell you (yet) because then we'd have to wipe your memory! First we want you to prove that you can take and execute orders: form the letter 'H' with 12 of your fellow Hartixs.",
